
doctype html
html
    head
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=0.8, maximum-scale=0.8')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato&display=swap', rel='stylesheet')
    style.
            #container {
                width: 800px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                background-color: #ffffff;
            }
            #header {
                width: 600px;
                padding: 25px 0 15px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                border-bottom: 1px solid #334750;
                text-align: center;
            }
            #header img {
                height: 40px;
                width: 128px;
            }
            #content {
                width: 600px;
                margin: 0 auto 40px;
                border-bottom: 1px solid #F8F9F9;
            }
            #content .name {
                margin: 50px 0 30px;
            }
            #content p,#content span {
                color: #334750;
                font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
                font-size: 18px;
                line-height: 25px;
            }
            a.btn {
                padding: 11px 13px;
                text-decoration: none;
                border-radius: 3px;
                background-color: #334750;
                color: #ffffff;
                font-family: Lato, sans-serif;
                font-size: 16px;
                line-height: 27px;
            }
            a.btn:link,
            a.btn:visited,
            a.btn:active {
                color: #ffffff;
            }
            #footer {
                padding: 34px 100px;
                background-color: #F8F9F9;
                color: #637381;
                font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 20px;
                text-align: center;
            }
            @media screen and (max-width: 575px) {
                #container {
                    width: 375px;
                }
                #header {
                    width: 335px;
                }
                #content {
                    width: 335px;
                }
                #content .name {
                    line-height: 40px;
                }
                #content P {
                    font-size: 16px;
                    line-height: 20px;
                }
                #footer {
                    padding: 34px 20px;
                    font-size: 16px;
                }
            }

    body
        #container(style=' width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff;')
            #header(style=' width: 600px; padding: 25px 0 15px; margin: 0 auto; border-bottom: 1px solid #334750; text-align: center;')
                img(style='height: 40px; width: 128px;' src='https://stage-nora-science37.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/public-email-assets/science37-logo-white.png', alt='logo')
            #content(style='width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 40px; border-bottom: 1px solid #F8F9F9;')
                p(style="color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; margin: 50px 0 30px") Hello #{firstname},
                p(style="color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px") Thank you for completing our online screening for the Sucrose Challenge Test and Sucrose Breath Test clinical research study. Based on your initial responses, we are unable to screen you further for participation in this particular clinical research study. &nbsp;
                p(style="color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px") If you have questions regarding why you are ineligible to proceed, you are welcome to contact one of our team members by calling or texting 877-726-3361 or email: headandneckad@science37.com. 
                p(style="color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px") We would love to stay in touch though if we have any other studies that you may be eligible for.
                span(style="color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px") To stay current on other clinical trials that are currently enrolling participants and perhaps sign up for those studies,please visit: 
                a(style="font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px" href='https://www.science37.com/patients/') https://www.science37.com/patients/
                p(style="color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px") Thank you for your time and interest! We look forward to discussing the study details with you!
                p(style="color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px") Kindly,
                    br
                    br
                    span(style="color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px") The Science 37 Patient Experience Team
